Class Weighted_analyzer

java.lang.Object
  com.cs408.forbes.chris.analysis.classes.Weighted_analyzer

public class Weighted_analyzer
extends java.lang.Object

This class follows the principles donated in the @see Basic_frequency_Analysis class as it focusing on single words however in a different manner it will focus on adding weights to the words in order to acheive the goal of a more balanced Keyword Density
